---
description: Keep everything maximally cheap & local-first
alwaysApply: true
glob: "**/*.py" "**/Dockerfile*" "README.md"
---

- Prefer local Docker containers (Memgraph, Redis) over any paid cloud service.
- Use 4-bit / 8-bit quantization for all LLM loading (bitsandbytes).
- Include fallback paths for CPU-only execution.
- Document free GPU rotation (Colab → Kaggle → Lightning AI) in scripts and README.
- Never assume paid APIs or high-RAM machines.